reviewText: This covers most angles of the mixtape game, and is just the right length.  History, Big Sellers, Where they were/are sold, styles of Mixtape, Bootlegging etc.  Features footage of the late Justo's Mixtape Awards and interviews with Justo, Kool Herc, Jazzy Joyce, DJ Clue, Doo Wop, Kay Slay, Kid Capri, Green Lantern, Brucie B, DJ Hollywood, and other DJs and MCs.  If you listen to mixtapes or want to know about this key area of Hip Hop then get this DVD.
